As the final hour of the fair approaches, announcement chimes signal this timing, coinciding with workshops on networking etiquette taking place in the adjoining classroom, providing further support to attendees. A whiteboard lists employers who are scheduling same-day interviews, and human resources teams jot notes on tablets while students introduce themselves and use tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database. As the event concludes, students exit with tote bags and a stack of business cards.

As the final hour of the fair approaches, announcement chimes signal this timing. Concurrently, workshops on networking etiquette are taking place in the adjoining classroom, enhancing the educational experience for attendees. Human resources teams jot notes on tablets while students introduce themselves and use kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews. As the event concludes, students exit with tote bags filled with business cards and resumes, while friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly.

As the event concludes, students exit with tote bags filled with business cards and resumes, while friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. As the final hour approaches, announcement chimes signal the closing time, coinciding with workshops on networking etiquette taking place in the adjoining classroom, providing further support to attendees. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, and human resources teams jot notes on tablets while students introduce themselves and use tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database. As the event concludes, students exit with tote bags and stacks of business cards.

Simultaneously, workshops on networking etiquette are taking place in the adjoining classroom, providing further support to attendees. Human resources teams jot notes on tablets while students introduce themselves and use tablets at kiosks to upload resumes to the fair database. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews. As the event concludes, students exit with tote bags and stacks of business cards, while friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly.
